sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant APP as 本机应用
    participant K as Linux Kernel
    participant TUN as tun0
    participant LRX as left_rx
    participant WK as worker_k
    participant ST as SessionTable_k
    participant DPI as DPI 插件
    participant RTX as right_tx_j
    participant RIO as tunnel socket
    participant SRV as Remote Server
    participant RRX as right_rx_j
    participant LTX as left_tx

    APP->>K: connect / send
    K->>TUN: 路由命中，写 IP 包
    LRX->>TUN: rx_burst 读包
    LRX->>LRX: 计算 hash(flow_key) mod N = k
    LRX->>WK: enqueue rx_ring (SPSC)
    WK->>WK: 解析 IP/TCP 头
    WK->>ST: lookup_or_create(flow_key)
    Note over ST: 新 session：分配 sid<br/>state=NEW, tunnel_idx=j
    WK->>DPI: feed(payload) 前 N 个包
    DPI-->>WK: app_proto = TLS / HTTP / ...
    WK->>WK: 封装隧道头 sid + meta + payload
    WK->>RTX: enqueue tx_ring (MPSC)
    RTX->>RIO: sendmmsg 批量
    RIO->>SRV: TCP/UDP/ICMP 报文

    SRV->>RIO: 响应报文
    RRX->>RIO: 读包并解隧道头
    RRX->>RRX: sid 算出 worker shard k
    RRX->>WK: enqueue back_ring (MPSC)
    WK->>ST: lookup(sid)
    WK->>WK: 重建 IP/TCP 头 NAT 回原五元组
    WK->>WK: 更新 stats / state
    WK->>LTX: enqueue left_tx.ring (MPSC)
    LTX->>TUN: tx_burst 写回
    TUN->>K: 内核协议栈处理
    K->>APP: recv 返回数据
